subject: Swimming
Olympic Games (2008)
Steroids
lead_paragraph: U.S.A. Swimming did not submit the names of Tara Kirk and Lara Jackson, the swimmers who finished third at the trials, behind Jessica Hardy, as alternates on its roster.
